<varlistentry id="options.StaysOnBack">
      <term><emphasis remap='I'>StaysOnBack</emphasis></term>
      <listitem>
<para>Places window in Layer -1, essentially forcing it to go under most other windows. Default Layer is 0. </para>
<para><emphasis remap='I'>NOTE: deprecated, use Layer instead.</emphasis></para>
      </listitem>
</varlistentry>
